00:59:58,116 --> 00:59:59,450
‚ÄéDo you like it?

694
01:00:02,578 --> 01:00:03,496
‚ÄéUncle.

695
01:00:04,455 --> 01:00:05,581
‚ÄéWhat now?

696
01:00:09,544 --> 01:00:10,878
‚ÄéMin-ji.

697
01:00:10,962 --> 01:00:14,590
‚ÄéIf you look to your left behind you,
‚Äéyou'll see an emergency exit.

698
01:00:15,717 --> 01:00:17,051
‚ÄéOn the count of three,

699
01:00:17,760 --> 01:00:20,930
‚ÄéI need you to run that way
‚Äéas fast as you can and don't look back.

700
01:00:21,597 --> 01:00:22,890
‚ÄéWhat are you talking about?

701
01:00:23,558 --> 01:00:25,560
‚Äé-What about you?
‚Äé-Me?

702
01:00:26,519 --> 01:00:29,939
‚ÄéI'm just going to say hi to those men
‚Äéand then catch up with you.

703
01:00:31,399 --> 01:00:33,359
‚ÄéYou can't do this alone.

704
01:00:33,443 --> 01:00:34,527
‚ÄéAll right. One‚Ä¶

705
01:00:35,820 --> 01:00:37,780
‚ÄéYou can shoot Sung Han-soo
‚Äéand claim it was an accident.

706
01:00:37,864 --> 01:00:38,990
‚ÄéDon't kill the girl.

707
01:00:39,073 --> 01:00:40,116
‚ÄéTwo‚Ä¶

708
01:00:40,199 --> 01:00:41,159
‚ÄéUncle!

709
01:00:51,335 --> 01:00:52,962
‚ÄéFire!

710
01:00:53,045 --> 01:00:54,046
‚ÄéThree.

711
01:01:02,180 --> 01:01:03,222
‚ÄéWhat the hell was that?!

712
01:01:07,059 --> 01:01:08,728
‚ÄéHe's always late.

713
01:01:11,022 --> 01:01:12,190
‚ÄéFlashbang.

714
01:01:16,736 --> 01:01:17,570
‚ÄéSmoke grenade.

715
01:01:30,166 --> 01:01:31,000
‚ÄéAttack.

716
01:01:50,895 --> 01:01:51,813
‚ÄéTactical team!

717
01:01:52,563 --> 01:01:54,440
‚ÄéRally at Zone C bunker!

718
01:02:05,368 --> 01:02:06,285
‚ÄéHey, get in!

719
01:02:06,369 --> 01:02:08,704
‚ÄéNice of you to finally show up.

720
01:02:08,788 --> 01:02:10,289
‚ÄéIt's okay, Min-ji.

721
01:02:21,259 --> 01:02:23,177
‚ÄéWhy aren't you getting in? Hurry up!

722
01:02:23,803 --> 01:02:26,138
‚ÄéHow can we get in if the doors won't open?

723
01:02:26,222 --> 01:02:27,682
‚ÄéWhat are we going to do?

724
01:02:38,109 --> 01:02:39,610
‚ÄéDamn it.

725
01:02:41,696 --> 01:02:42,864
‚ÄéYou're shooting blanks, aren't you?

726
01:02:47,994 --> 01:02:49,036
‚ÄéThey're blank rounds.

727
01:02:50,997 --> 01:02:51,956
‚ÄéHey, take cover!

728
01:02:53,666 --> 01:02:54,750
‚ÄéThey're blank rounds! Fire!

729
01:02:56,377 --> 01:02:57,503
‚ÄéHey, Min-ji!

730
01:02:58,629 --> 01:03:01,340
‚ÄéOh, for crying out loud! My car!

731
01:03:03,801 --> 01:03:06,262
‚ÄéHey, you should've brought some live ammo!

732
01:03:06,345 --> 01:03:08,890
‚ÄéWhy did you bring all blank rounds?

733
01:03:08,973 --> 01:03:10,266
‚ÄéThey caught on right away.

734
01:03:10,349 --> 01:03:12,268
‚ÄéI did bring live ammo!

735
01:03:12,351 --> 01:03:14,770
‚ÄéBut I can't go around
‚Äékilling my juniors, can I?

736
01:03:18,232 --> 01:03:19,901
‚ÄéJeez, my car, man!

737
01:03:28,284 --> 01:03:29,452
‚ÄéThis won't do, huh?

738
01:03:30,328 --> 01:03:31,162
‚ÄéHere.

739
01:03:33,205 --> 01:03:34,040
‚ÄéChoose one!

740
01:03:35,166 --> 01:03:38,044
‚ÄéI can't choose
‚Äébecause I love both of them!

741
01:03:38,127 --> 01:03:40,129
‚Äé-Choose one.
‚Äé-You want to have a shootout?

742
01:03:42,173 --> 01:03:43,341
‚ÄéHold your fire!

743
01:03:55,436 --> 01:03:56,604
‚ÄéHey, Park Jin-cheol.

744
01:03:57,730 --> 01:03:58,564
‚ÄéNow what?

745
01:03:59,231 --> 01:04:00,358
‚ÄéYou want us to continue?

746
01:04:12,119 --> 01:04:13,663
‚ÄéThis is a white flag.

747
01:04:13,746 --> 01:04:14,580
‚ÄéWe surrender!

748
01:04:15,289 --> 01:04:16,749
‚ÄéWe're coming out, so don't shoot!

749
01:04:18,960 --> 01:04:19,919
‚ÄéWe're coming!

750
01:04:21,504 --> 01:04:22,630
‚ÄéNice and slow!

751
01:04:23,714 --> 01:04:24,882
‚ÄéSlowly!

752
01:04:24,966 --> 01:04:26,217
‚ÄéSlowly!

753
01:04:26,801 --> 01:04:28,010
‚ÄéWhy are there so many of you?

754
01:04:28,636 --> 01:04:30,638
‚ÄéAll of you just to catch the three of us?

755
01:04:34,058 --> 01:04:36,894
‚ÄéI saved you from drowning,
‚Äéand you shoot live ammo?

756
01:04:37,520 --> 01:04:39,271
‚ÄéThere's a kid here too, you mole rat.

757
01:04:39,355 --> 01:04:42,858
‚ÄéYou return to your old stomping grounds
‚Äéafter all this time, wreck the place,

758
01:04:42,942 --> 01:04:43,818
‚Äéand expect me to sit back?

759
01:04:44,735 --> 01:04:45,569
‚ÄéTake her.

760
01:04:45,653 --> 01:04:46,779
‚Äé-Yes, sir.
‚Äé-Yes, sir.

761
01:04:48,489 --> 01:04:49,532
‚ÄéAll of you!

762
01:04:50,616 --> 01:04:51,492
‚ÄéDrop your guns!

763
01:05:02,086 --> 01:05:03,045
‚ÄéWhat are you doing?

764
01:05:04,338 --> 01:05:06,048
‚ÄéI said drop your guns!

765
01:05:53,804 --> 01:05:54,889
‚ÄéDad?

766
01:06:06,776 --> 01:06:07,902
‚ÄéDad!

767
01:06:07,985 --> 01:06:08,986
‚ÄéWait here.

768
01:06:11,489 --> 01:06:12,323
‚ÄéMin-ji.

769
01:06:14,658 --> 01:06:15,743
‚ÄéI'm here.

770
01:06:22,166 --> 01:06:23,334
‚ÄéLet's go home now.

771
01:06:23,918 --> 01:06:24,919
‚ÄéDad‚Ä¶

772
01:07:08,254 --> 01:07:11,966
‚ÄéAGENT KIM REACTIVATED

773
01:07:13,551 --> 01:07:15,845
‚ÄéI'm here now, so don't worry.

774
01:07:18,472 --> 01:07:20,474
‚ÄéI'm going to witness the end myself.

775
01:07:20,558 --> 01:07:22,434
‚ÄéJust take a quick nap, hero!

776
01:07:23,435 --> 01:07:26,147
‚ÄéAn attempted cover-up and a kidnapping‚Ä¶

777
01:07:26,230 --> 01:07:28,858
‚ÄéWe should take this chance
‚Äéto get rid of him first.

778
01:07:28,941 --> 01:07:30,526
‚ÄéI'm sure you weren't
‚Äéin your right mind either,

779
01:07:30,609 --> 01:07:31,944
‚Äétrying to find your daughter.

780
01:07:32,027 --> 01:07:35,281
‚ÄéToday will be the last time
‚ÄéAgent Kim sees Min-ji.

781
01:07:36,115 --> 01:07:37,199
‚ÄéDad!

782
01:07:39,702 --> 01:07:41,370
‚ÄéFor Min-ji's sake,

783
01:07:41,453 --> 01:07:42,621
‚ÄéI'm going to

784
01:07:42,705 --> 01:07:43,831
‚Äéend you.

785
01:07:46,083 --> 01:07:49,003
‚ÄéSubtitle translation by: Jenny Kim

